# ===============================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# ===============================

# If you encounter API quota limits:
# - Set MOCK_MODE=true for development
# - Check your billing and usage limits
# - Try a different model or provider

# For connection issues:
# - Verify your API key is correct
# - Check the base URL matches your provider
# - Ensure your firewall allows outbound HTTPS
